name: hyperlink
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "hyperlink" %}
{% set version = "17.3.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: bc4ffdbde9bdad204d507bd8f554f16bba82dd356f6130cb16f41422909c33bc

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - hyperlink

about:
  home: https://github.com/python-hyper/hyperlink
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Immutable, Pythonic, correct URLs.
  dev_url: https://github.com/python-hyper/hyperlink
  doc_url: http://hyperlink.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - isuruf
